author: jukka
msg: TIKA-263: Core parser classes duplicated in the tika-parser and tika-core jar files.

Duplication was caused by the Maven bundle plugin automatically embedding packages matching the Export-Package setting. Dropping those settings causes the plugin to simply include and export all packages in the source tree of this component.
